snippet.textDisplay:
Hello Rick, I live in Mexico and I am a low handicapper, but always looking for any improvement, I currenlty use the M6 driver and it has been a huge improvement over my previous Taylor Made M2 driver.
I have been watching your videos for a while (almost a year now) and all are very entertaining and very professional and provide good information for any equipment change I would like to make.. For example, I used to play only Prov1 and Prov1X balls but now, when I play in golf courses with long par 4´s I use the AVX thanks mainly for your review of this ball, the low spin gives me 10 extra yards on medium and long irons.
After this review I will porbably wait a littel before changing my trusty M6, maybe we will see a better SIM after summer or for 2021?
One comment about the SIM logo: When you place the head upside down it reads WIS (Winning is Simpler) maybe with this driver?
